00:34:23.033 --> 00:34:23.833
Then what about me?

00:34:24.833 --> 00:34:26.200
Sorry, neither puppies and kittens.

00:34:28.100 --> 00:34:30.766
♪And we will take a cup of kindness yet♪

00:34:30.800 --> 00:34:38.033
♪For old long past♪

00:34:45.433 --> 00:34:46.700
We could go on tour.

00:34:47.600 --> 00:34:49.300
