00:34:50.933 --> 00:34:52.933
I just posted on Soul App.

00:34:52.933 --> 00:34:55.266
It's good news for new users.

00:34:55.266 --> 00:34:56.333
Make sure you check it out.

00:34:56.366 --> 00:34:57.300
