00:35:50.100 --> 00:35:51.366
You sing really well too.

00:35:51.366 --> 00:35:51.866
Me?

00:35:51.900 --> 00:35:52.400
Right.

00:35:52.400 --> 00:35:53.000
I...

00:35:54.633 --> 00:35:55.733
[Their Gravity Tag]
Namiya...

00:35:56.033 --> 00:35:58.566
[Checking Zhaoyu Zhang's Moment]

00:35:58.800 --> 00:36:00.533
He's got that trendy vibe.

00:36:00.566 --> 00:36:01.633
He's really handsome.

00:36:02.133 --> 00:36:04.066
