00:36:06.166 --> 00:36:07.033
Her posts are really fun.

00:36:07.033 --> 00:36:08.333
I think she's a fun person.

00:36:11.100 --> 00:36:13.366
[Their Gravity Tag. Eon's Moment]
He says he's athletic.

00:36:14.333 --> 00:36:15.566
It is...

00:36:15.566 --> 00:36:16.900
He runs 5 km races.

00:36:16.933 --> 00:36:18.400
