00:36:18.400 --> 00:36:19.300
Lily.

00:36:19.833 --> 00:36:22.500
[Checking Lily's Moment]

00:36:22.766 --> 00:36:24.166
Joining any clubs later?

00:36:25.233 --> 00:36:26.033
Not sure.

00:36:26.033 --> 00:36:27.733
Today's classes were so fun.

00:36:32.133 --> 00:36:33.133
