00:37:19.133 --> 00:37:22.033
[Sean]

00:37:22.300 --> 00:37:25.000
Hi.

00:37:25.000 --> 00:37:25.700
Hi, I'm...

00:37:25.733 --> 00:37:26.766
Sean, right?

00:37:26.766 --> 00:37:27.266
Yeah.

00:37:27.300 --> 00:37:28.166
Hi, I'm Olivia.

00:37:28.166 --> 00:37:28.766
You're Olivia, right?

00:37:28.766 --> 00:37:29.800
Hi.

00:37:30.200 --> 00:37:30.666
Have a seat.

00:37:31.033 --> 00:37:32.633
You sit there, right?

00:37:32.633 --> 00:37:33.633
Then you can sit here.

00:37:33.633 --> 00:37:34.966
Okay, you want to sit...

00:37:35.000 --> 00:37:35.600
I'll sit here.

00:37:35.600 --> 00:37:36.233
Then I'll sit there.

00:37:36.233 --> 00:37:36.900
Okay.

00:37:39.366 --> 00:37:40.100
Hi.

00:37:41.200 --> 00:37:42.533
Did you expect me to invite you?

00:37:44.700 --> 00:37:45.366
Probably not.

00:37:45.966 --> 00:37:47.300
No? Okay then.

00:37:47.333 --> 00:37:48.166
Well, I did.

00:37:50.833 --> 00:37:52.066
Let's eat.

00:37:52.100 --> 00:37:53.366
Which one do you want?

00:37:53.366 --> 00:37:55.400
You pick. I'm good with anything.

00:37:55.400 --> 00:37:57.933
