00:37:57.966 --> 00:37:58.800
Can you handle spicy food?

00:37:58.800 --> 00:37:59.900
Yeah.

00:37:59.933 --> 00:38:00.766
You are...

00:38:01.733 --> 00:38:02.466
Let me introduce myself.

00:38:02.500 --> 00:38:03.633
My name is Sean.

00:38:03.633 --> 00:38:05.266
I actually grew up in Guangzhou.

00:38:05.300 --> 00:38:06.366
My dad is from Zhejiang Province.

00:38:07.566 --> 00:38:09.800
But my grandma is from Guizhou Province.

00:38:09.800 --> 00:38:11.000
So I can handle spicy food.

00:38:11.000 --> 00:38:12.533
So you usually live in...?

00:38:12.566 --> 00:38:13.300
Guangzhou, yeah.

00:38:13.700 --> 00:38:14.766
I study in Hong Kong, China.

00:38:14.766 --> 00:38:16.100
I'm a senior at CUHK.

00:38:17.366 --> 00:38:19.500
I'm from Shanghai.

00:38:20.500 --> 00:38:21.800
I did my undergrad in Shanghai.

00:38:22.333 --> 00:38:25.066
I just got my master degree from the UK.

00:38:25.100 --> 00:38:27.766
[Olivia]
So I may be a bit older than you.

00:38:27.766 --> 00:38:29.366
I was born in September 2003.

00:38:29.366 --> 00:38:30.066
Actually, it's because I

00:38:30.566 --> 00:38:32.800
did an extra year of kindergarten.

00:38:32.800 --> 00:38:35.800
[Curious]
You stayed an extra year?

00:38:35.800 --> 00:38:37.633
My mom just felt that

00:38:37.633 --> 00:38:39.166
