00:38:39.200 --> 00:38:40.300
would give me an edge.

00:38:40.966 --> 00:38:42.166
So, is there one?

00:38:42.166 --> 00:38:43.166
Maybe in first grade.

00:38:43.166 --> 00:38:45.266
Not in second or third.

00:38:45.300 --> 00:38:45.566
Okay.

00:38:45.566 --> 00:38:46.366
Eat first. Go ahead.

00:38:46.366 --> 00:38:46.866
Go on.

00:38:47.833 --> 00:38:49.566
Did I totally blow my intro?

00:38:50.833 --> 00:38:53.666
[Sean]
I think you were more calm

00:38:53.700 --> 00:38:55.200
than all of us, basically.

00:38:56.233 --> 00:38:56.566
You

00:38:56.600 --> 00:38:59.033
introduced yourself
in front of all of us alone.

00:38:59.033 --> 00:38:59.966
And, yeah.

00:39:00.000 --> 00:39:02.666
Then after my introduction,

00:39:02.700 --> 00:39:03.600
what was your first impression

00:39:03.600 --> 00:39:05.433
of me as a person?

00:39:08.000 --> 00:39:09.100
I think everyone felt that you were

00:39:09.133 --> 00:39:10.733
really lovely and easygoing.

00:39:10.733 --> 00:39:13.133
[Lovely and easygoing]

00:39:13.133 --> 00:39:14.400
Thank you.

00:39:14.400 --> 00:39:15.800
Even with all that pressure,

00:39:15.800 --> 00:39:17.533
I still got such high praise.

00:39:17.566 --> 00:39:19.433
[To be fair]
Your intro was fresh.

00:39:19.533 --> 00:39:20.333
You know,

00:39:20.333 --> 00:39:23.033
it was you and your little pig,
Zhumi, right?

00:39:23.033 --> 00:39:24.500
Yeah, because my last name is Zhu.

00:39:25.900 --> 00:39:26.533
Right.

00:39:26.533 --> 00:39:27.566
Olivia Zhu.

00:39:30.133 --> 00:39:32.166
[I remember]

00:39:32.500 --> 00:39:33.733
so after coming here,

00:39:33.733 --> 00:39:35.333
was it hard to adjust?

00:39:35.333 --> 00:39:36.333
Starting today,

00:39:36.333 --> 00:39:37.600
I feel like with everyone,

00:39:37.600 --> 00:39:39.100
it all feels pretty natural.

00:39:39.133 --> 00:39:40.200
But when I first got here,

00:39:40.200 --> 00:39:41.666
I was nervous.

00:39:44.400 --> 00:39:46.033
So are you still nervous now?

00:39:46.033 --> 00:39:46.933
I'm not nervous now.

00:39:46.966 --> 00:39:47.600
Okay.

00:39:47.600 --> 00:39:48.400
Have something to eat.

00:39:48.400 --> 00:39:49.666
That should help you relax.

00:39:49.700 --> 00:39:50.733
Yeah.

00:39:54.766 --> 00:39:56.433
It caught it, my skirt caught it.

00:39:57.300 --> 00:39:57.933
No, it didn't.

00:39:58.966 --> 00:39:59.700
Here.

00:39:59.733 --> 00:40:00.766
[Hands over tissue]
Thank you.

00:40:01.633 --> 00:40:02.833
You carry tissues with you?

00:40:02.833 --> 00:40:05.700
Yeah, I've had a runny nose lately.

00:40:05.733 --> 00:40:06.566
It's really cold here.

00:40:06.566 --> 00:40:08.066
[Keep this first]
Here, take it. You may need it later.

00:40:08.966 --> 00:40:09.466
You don't have to

00:40:09.500 --> 00:40:10.300
